						<div class="postbody">Assuming that before that you wrote to $20 and $00 to $2006 and then you wrote the loop, after that you could write $21 and $00 to $2006 and repeat the loop, e.g.:
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">&nbsp;lda #$20 ;Here we're writing to $2000<br />&nbsp;sta $2006<br />&nbsp;lda #$00<br />&nbsp;sta $2006<br /><br />&nbsp;ldx #$00<br /><br />loop1:<br />&nbsp;lda titlescreengfx,x<br />&nbsp;sta $2007<br />&nbsp;inx<br />&nbsp;cpx #$00<br />&nbsp;bne loop1<br /><br />&nbsp;lda #$21 ;And here - to $2100 - $100 bytes later<br />&nbsp;sta $2006<br />&nbsp;lda #$00<br />&nbsp;sta $2006<br /><br />loop2:<br />&nbsp;lda titlescreengfx,x<br />&nbsp;sta $2007<br />&nbsp;inx<br />&nbsp;cpx #$00<br />&nbsp;bne loop2</div>Etc.</div>

